    "html": "<div class=\"B1_text_xin\" id=\"cont\">\n<div style=\"text-align: center\"><img alt=\"&#x4F5B;&#x8BF4;&#x76C2;&#x5170;&#x76C6;&#x7ECF;&#x6CE8;&#x97F3;\" src=\"https://www.liaotuo.com/uploadfile/2019/0214/20190214014843876.png\" style=\"height: 300px; width: 208px;\" title=\"&#x4F5B;&#x8BF4;&#x76C2;&#x5170;&#x76C6;&#x7ECF;&#x6CE8;&#x97F3;\" /></div>\n<h3>（如发现注音有错误，请您联系我们，便于我们及时纠正，qq：1300659095。<a href=\"/remen/ganen.html\" class=\"keylink\" target=\"_blank\">感恩</a>）</h3>\n<p><span>wen<br />&#13;\n闻</span><span>ru<br />&#13;\n如</span><span>shi<br />&#13;\n是</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>yi<br />&#13;\n一</span><span>shi<br />&#13;\n时</span><span>fo<br />&#13;\n佛</span><span>zai<br />&#13;\n在</span><span>she<br />&#13;\n舍</span><span>wei<br />&#13;\n卫</span><span>guo<br />&#13;\n国</span><span>qi<br />&#13;\n祇</span><span>shu<br />&#13;\n树</span><span>gu<br />&#13;\n孤</span><span>du<br />&#13;\n独</span><span>yuan<br />&#13;\n园</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span><span>da<br />&#13;\n大</span><span>mu<br />&#13;\n目</span><span>jian<br />&#13;\n犍</span><span>lian<br />&#13;\n连</span><span>shi<br />&#13;\n始</span><span>de<br />&#13;\n得</span><span>liu<br />&#13;\n六</span><span>tong<br />&#13;\n通</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>yu<br />&#13;\n欲</span><span>du<br />&#13;\n度</span><span>fu<br />&#13;\n父</span><span>mu<br />&#13;\n母</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>bao<br />&#13;\n报</span><span>ru<br />&#13;\n乳</span><span>bu<br />&#13;\n哺</span><span>zhi<br />&#13;\n之</span><span>en<br />&#13;\n恩</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>ji<br />&#13;\n即</span><span>yi<br />&#13;\n以</span><span>dao<br />&#13;\n道</span><span>yan<br />&#13;\n眼</span><span>guan<br />&#13;\n观</span><span>shi<br />&#13;\n视</span><span>shi<br />&#13;\n世</span><span>jian<br />&#13;\n间</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span><span>jian<br />&#13;\n见</span><span>qi<br />&#13;\n其</span><span>wang<br />&#13;\n亡</span><span>mu<br />&#13;\n母</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>sheng<br />&#13;\n生</span><span>e<br />&#13;\n饿</span><span>gui<br />&#13;\n鬼</span><span>zhong<br />&#13;\n中</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>bu<br />&#13;\n不</span><span>jian<br />&#13;\n见</span><span>yin<br />&#13;\n饮</span><span>shi<br />&#13;\n食</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>pi<br />&#13;\n皮</span><span>gu<br />&#13;\n骨</span><span>lian<br />&#13;\n连</span><span>li<br />&#13;\n立</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span><span>mu<br />&#13;\n目</span><span>lian<br />&#13;\n连</span><span>bei<br />&#13;\n悲</span><span>ai<br />&#13;\n哀</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>ji<br />&#13;\n即</span><span>yi<br />&#13;\n以</span><span>bo<br />&#13;\n钵</span><span>cheng<br />&#13;\n盛</span><span>fan<br />&#13;\n饭</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>wang<br />&#13;\n往</span><span>xiang<br />&#13;\n饷</span><span>qi<br />&#13;\n其</span><span>mu<br />&#13;\n母</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span><span>mu<br />&#13;\n母</span><span>de<br />&#13;\n得</span><span>bo<br />&#13;\n钵</span><span>fan<br />&#13;\n饭</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>bian<br />&#13;\n便</span><span>yi<br />&#13;\n以</span><span>zuo<br />&#13;\n左</span><span>shou<br />&#13;\n手</span><span>zhang<br />&#13;\n障</span><span>bo<br />&#13;\n钵</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>you<br />&#13;\n右</span><span>shou<br />&#13;\n手</span><span>tuan<br />&#13;\n抟</span><span>shi<br />&#13;\n食</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>shi<br />&#13;\n食</span><span>wei<br />&#13;\n未</span><span>ru<br />&#13;\n入</span><span>kou<br />&#13;\n口</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>hua<br />&#13;\n化</span><span>cheng<br />&#13;\n成</span><span>huo<br />&#13;\n火</span><span>tan<br />&#13;\n炭</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>sui<br />&#13;\n遂</span><span>bu<br />&#13;\n不</span><span>de<br />&#13;\n得</span><span>shi<br />&#13;\n食</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span><span>mu<br />&#13;\n目</span><span>lian<br />&#13;\n连</span><span>da<br />&#13;\n大</span><span>jiao<br />&#13;\n叫</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>bei<br />&#13;\n悲</span><span>hao<br />&#13;\n号</span><span>ti<br />&#13;\n涕</span><span>qi<br />&#13;\n泣</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>chi<br />&#13;\n驰</span><span>huan<br />&#13;\n还</span><span>bai<br />&#13;\n白</span><span>fo<br />&#13;\n佛</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>ju<br />&#13;\n具</span><span>chen<br />&#13;\n陈</span><span>ru<br />&#13;\n如</span><span>ci<br />&#13;\n此</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>fo<br />&#13;\n佛</span><span>yan<br />&#13;\n言</span><span>：<br />&#13;\n：</span><span>ru<br />&#13;\n汝</span><span>mu<br />&#13;\n母</span><span>zui<br />&#13;\n罪</span><span>gen<br />&#13;\n根</span><span>shen<br />&#13;\n深</span><span>jie<br />&#13;\n结</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>fei<br />&#13;\n非</span><span>ru<br />&#13;\n汝</span><span>yi<br />&#13;\n一</span><span>ren<br />&#13;\n人</span><span>li<br />&#13;\n力</span><span>suo<br />&#13;\n所</span><span>nai<br />&#13;\n奈</span><span>he<br />&#13;\n何</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span><span>ru<br />&#13;\n汝</span><span>sui<br />&#13;\n虽</span><span>xiao<br />&#13;\n孝</span><span>shun<br />&#13;\n顺</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>sheng<br />&#13;\n声</span><span>dong<br />&#13;\n动</span><span>tian<br />&#13;\n天</span><span>di<br />&#13;\n地</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>tian<br />&#13;\n天</span><span>shen<br />&#13;\n神</span><span>、<br />&#13;\n、</span><span>di<br />&#13;\n地</span><span>qi<br />&#13;\n祇</span><span>、<br />&#13;\n、</span><span>xie<br />&#13;\n邪</span><span>mo<br />&#13;\n魔</span><span>、<br />&#13;\n、</span><span>wai<br />&#13;\n外</span><span>dao<br />&#13;\n道</span><span>dao<br />&#13;\n道</span><span>shi<br />&#13;\n士</span><span>、<br />&#13;\n、</span><span>si<br />&#13;\n四</span><span>tian<br />&#13;\n天</span><span>wang<br />&#13;\n王</span><span>shen<br />&#13;\n神</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>yi<br />&#13;\n亦</span><span>bu<br />&#13;\n不</span><span>neng<br />&#13;\n能</span><span>nai<br />&#13;\n奈</span><span>he<br />&#13;\n何</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span><span>dang<br />&#13;\n当</span><span>ru<br />&#13;\n须</span><span>shi<br />&#13;\n十</span><span>fang<br />&#13;\n方</span><span>zhong<br />&#13;\n众</span><span>seng<br />&#13;\n僧</span><span>wei<br />&#13;\n威</span><span>shen<br />&#13;\n神</span><span>zhi<br />&#13;\n之</span><span>li<br />&#13;\n力</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>nai<br />&#13;\n乃</span><span>de<br />&#13;\n得</span><span>jie<br />&#13;\n解</span><span>tuo<br />&#13;\n脱</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>wu<br />&#13;\n吾</span><span>jin<br />&#13;\n今</span><span>dang<br />&#13;\n当</span><span>shuo<br />&#13;\n说</span><span>jiu<br />&#13;\n救</span><span>ji<br />&#13;\n济</span><span>zhi<br />&#13;\n之</span><span>fa<br />&#13;\n法</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>ling<br />&#13;\n令</span><span>yi<br />&#13;\n一</span><span>qie<br />&#13;\n切</span><span>nan<br />&#13;\n难</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>jie<br />&#13;\n皆</span><span>li<br />&#13;\n离</span><span>you<br />&#13;\n忧</span><span>ku<br />&#13;\n苦</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span></p>\n<p><span>fo<br />&#13;\n佛</span><span>gao<br />&#13;\n告</span><span>mu<br />&#13;\n目</span><span>lian<br />&#13;\n连</span><span>：<br />&#13;\n：</span><span>shi<br />&#13;\n十</span><span>fang<br />&#13;\n方</span><span>zhong<br />&#13;\n众</span><span>seng<br />&#13;\n僧</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>qi<br />&#13;\n七</span><span>yue<br />&#13;\n月</span><span>shi<br />&#13;\n十</span><span>wu<br />&#13;\n五</span><span>ri<br />&#13;\n日</span><span>seng<br />&#13;\n僧</span><span>zi<br />&#13;\n自</span><span>zi<br />&#13;\n恣</span><span>shi<br />&#13;\n时</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>dang<br />&#13;\n当</span><span>wei<br />&#13;\n为</span><span>qi<br />&#13;\n七</span><span>shi<br />&#13;\n世</span><span>fu<br />&#13;\n父</span><span>mu<br />&#13;\n母</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>ji<br />&#13;\n及</span><span>xian<br />&#13;\n现</span><span>zai<br />&#13;\n在</span><span>fu<br />&#13;\n父</span><span>mu<br />&#13;\n母</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>e<br />&#13;\n厄</span><span>nan<br />&#13;\n难</span><span>zhong<br />&#13;\n中</span><span>zhe<br />&#13;\n者</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>ju<br />&#13;\n具</span><span>fan<br />&#13;\n饭</span><span>bai<br />&#13;\n百</span><span>wei<br />&#13;\n味</span><span>wu<br />&#13;\n五</span><span>guo<br />&#13;\n果</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>ji<br />&#13;\n汲</span><span>guan<br />&#13;\n灌</span><span>pen<br />&#13;\n盆</span><span>qi<br />&#13;\n器</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>xiang<br />&#13;\n香</span><span>you<br />&#13;\n油</span><span>ding<br />&#13;\n锭</span><span>zhu<br />&#13;\n烛</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>chuang<br />&#13;\n床</span><span>fu<br />&#13;\n敷</span><span>wo<br />&#13;\n卧</span><span>ju<br />&#13;\n具</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>jin<br />&#13;\n尽</span><span>shi<br />&#13;\n世</span><span>gan<br />&#13;\n甘</span><span>mei<br />&#13;\n美</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>yi<br />&#13;\n以</span><span>zhu<br />&#13;\n著</span><span>pen<br />&#13;\n盆</span><span>zhong<br />&#13;\n中</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>gong<br />&#13;\n供</span><span>yang<br />&#13;\n养</span><span>shi<br />&#13;\n十</span><span>fang<br />&#13;\n方</span><span>da<br />&#13;\n大</span><span>de<br />&#13;\n德</span><span>zhong<br />&#13;\n众</span><span>seng<br />&#13;\n僧</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span><span>dang<br />&#13;\n当</span><span>ci<br />&#13;\n此</span><span>zhi<br />&#13;\n之</span><span>ri<br />&#13;\n日</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>yi<br />&#13;\n一</span><span>qie<br />&#13;\n切</span><span>sheng<br />&#13;\n圣</span><span>zhong<br />&#13;\n众</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>huo<br />&#13;\n或</span><span>zai<br />&#13;\n在</span><span>shan<br />&#13;\n山</span><span>jian<br />&#13;\n间</span><span>chan<br />&#13;\n禅</span><span>ding<br />&#13;\n定</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>huo<br />&#13;\n或</span><span>de<br />&#13;\n得</span><span>si<br />&#13;\n四</span><span>dao<br />&#13;\n道</span><span>guo<br />&#13;\n果</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>huo<br />&#13;\n或</span><span>zai<br />&#13;\n在</span><span>shu<br />&#13;\n树</span><span>xia<br />&#13;\n下</span><span>jing<br />&#13;\n经</span><span>xing<br />&#13;\n行</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>huo<br />&#13;\n或</span><span>liu<br />&#13;\n六</span><span>tong<br />&#13;\n通</span><span>zi<br />&#13;\n自</span><span>zai<br />&#13;\n在</span><span>jiao<br />&#13;\n教</span><span>hua<br />&#13;\n化</span><span>sheng<br />&#13;\n声</span><span>wen<br />&#13;\n闻</span><span>yuan<br />&#13;\n缘</span><span>jue<br />&#13;\n觉</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>huo<br />&#13;\n或</span><span>shi<br />&#13;\n十</span><span>di<br />&#13;\n地</span><span>pu<br />&#13;\n菩</span><span>sa<br />&#13;\n萨</span><span>da<br />&#13;\n大</span><span>ren<br />&#13;\n人</span><span>quan<br />&#13;\n权</span><span>xian<br />&#13;\n现</span><span>bi<br />&#13;\n比</span><span>qiu<br />&#13;\n丘</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>zai<br />&#13;\n在</span><span>zhong<br />&#13;\n众</span><span>zhong<br />&#13;\n中</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>jie<br />&#13;\n皆</span><span>tong<br />&#13;\n同</span><span>yi<br />&#13;\n一</span><span>xin<br />&#13;\n心</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>shou<br />&#13;\n受</span><span>bo<br />&#13;\n钵</span><span>he<br />&#13;\n和</span><span>luo<br />&#13;\n罗</span><span>fan<br />&#13;\n饭</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>ju<br />&#13;\n具</span><span>qing<br />&#13;\n清</span><span>jing<br />&#13;\n净</span><span>jie<br />&#13;\n戒</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>sheng<br />&#13;\n圣</span><span>zhong<br />&#13;\n众</span><span>zhi<br />&#13;\n之</span><span>dao<br />&#13;\n道</span><span>，<br />&#13;\n，</span><span>qi<br />&#13;\n其</span><span>de<br />&#13;\n德</span><span>wang<br />&#13;\n汪</span><span>yang<br />&#13;\n洋</span><span>。<br />&#13;\n。</span><span>qi<br />&#13;\n其</span><span>y